        <title type="html"><![CDATA[颈椎康复小攻略]]></title>
        <id>https://kang-shawn.github.io/post/jing-zhui-kang-fu-xiao-gong-lue/</id>
        <link href="https://kang-shawn.github.io/post/jing-zhui-kang-fu-xiao-gong-lue/">
        </link>
        <updated>2020-08-16T11:26:23.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="一-错误姿势及如何纠正">一、错误姿势及如何纠正</h2>
<h4 id="错误姿势一">错误姿势一</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-1aaeb58dd146993f.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>纠正：头和胳膊休息的时候向后伸。</p>
<h4 id="错误姿势二">错误姿势二</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="2"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-a55149eacce317a0.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ul>
<li>坐的时间不要超过40分钟，专业说法是在引起不适感之前起身活动</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="错误姿势三">错误姿势三</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-79af8832dc403092.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ul>
<li>
<p>两侧屁股高低是一样的</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>腰和背尽量是直的，或者靠在座椅上，腰后面也可以放个小垫子</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>眼睛和电脑屏幕是平行的</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="二-五分钟的颈椎大保健">二、五分钟的颈椎大保健</h2>
<h4 id="21-拉伸斜方肌上束">2.1 拉伸斜方肌上束</h4>
<p>肩膀和颈椎两侧的肌肉</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="4"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-873fa7f6dbf304f2.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><a href="http://www.miaopai.com/show/~3HuYj0dvSk-yBadI0ZSOA__.htm">视频地址</a></p>
<p>每一侧持续15s，共三组。</p>
<h4 id="22拉伸胸锁乳突肌">2.2拉伸胸锁乳突肌</h4>
<p>还可以治疗双下巴</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="5"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-11885bfc45070795.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><a href="http://www.miaopai.com/show/IodqnkF5kFj8fOSEF~fvbw__.htm">视频地址</a></p>
<h4 id="23自我手法放松颈后肌群">2.3自我手法放松颈后肌群</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="6"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-22622b9ebe17ccf9.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><a href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/8saJCZgxR-YqLpaulszAzQ">视频地址</a></p>
<p>每组左右各十次，共3组。</p>
<h4 id="24w练习菱形肌">2.4“W”练习菱形肌</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="7"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-2398c8f251e265e7.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><a href="http://www.miaopai.com/show/QJE8tNtkFMVwFUKVRS1Hvg__.htm">视频地址</a></p>
<p>每组12-20个，共三组，分为上半部分和下半部分。</p>
<h2 id="三-如何系统有效康复颈椎">三、如何系统有效康复颈椎</h2>
<h3 id="1-泡沫轴放松枕骨下缘-颈后-肩背肌肉">1 泡沫轴放松枕骨下缘、颈后、肩背肌肉</h3>
<p><a href="http://www.miaopai.com/show/wimrFGItqbu0hycfBDsY8g__.htm">视频地址</a></p>
<h3 id="2激活练习">2.激活练习</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<h5 id="颈深屈服激活练习">颈深屈服激活练习</h5>
</li>
</ul>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="8"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-b7757f39a0e199db.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>躺下仰卧位，后缩双下巴，头给床面一个作用力，每次保持6s，每组6个，做3组。</p>
<ul>
<li>
<h5 id="颈伸肌激活练习">颈伸肌激活练习</h5>
</li>
</ul>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="9"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-cc998e3ca71e8d44.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>跪姿，一开始头背一条直线，头慢慢后仰到极限，靠头的自重。仰到最后面坚持6s，每组8个，3组。</p>
<ul>
<li>
<h5 id="颈椎旋转肌肉激活">颈椎旋转肌肉激活</h5>
</li>
</ul>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="10"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-d3f7c5089e49bc41.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>起始姿势：躺着仰卧，双下巴收起下颌，然后仰头</p>
<p>然后头往左侧旋转45度，缓慢回到中立位，再往右侧旋转45度，左右各6次，共三组。</p>
<h3 id="3强化薄弱肌群">3.强化薄弱肌群</h3>
<h4 id="31仰头夹背">3.1仰头夹背</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="11"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-ab7edf30130d4cd7.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>静态姿势，双臂微张，拇指向前，掌心相对，然后胳膊尽量向后伸，肩胛骨收缩，头向后仰，仰到极限。每次静止15s，共三组。</p>
<h4 id="32-w-练习菱形肌">3.2 W 练习菱形肌</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="12"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-8d8436f2abeec347.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><a href="http://www.miaopai.com/show/QJE8tNtkFMVwFUKVRS1Hvg__.htm">视频地址</a></p>
<p>每组12-20个，共三组，分为上半部分和下半部分。</p>
<h4 id="33-气场大法练习菱形肌-斜方肌中束下束">3.3 气场大法练习菱形肌、斜方肌中束下束</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="13"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-c2224e227793f239.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>每组10个，最大强度处上下再10次，3-5组，组与组间休息30s-1min</p>
<p><a href="http://www.miaopai.com/show/qIQFygorwYVXU2YTurodtw__.htm">视频地址</a></p>
<h4 id="34肩外旋薄弱集群">3.4肩外旋薄弱集群</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="14"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-be28933f8fb89932.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<h3 id="4拉伸紧张肌肉恢复弹性和伸展性">4.拉伸紧张肌肉，恢复弹性和伸展性</h3>
<h4 id="41拉伸斜方肌上束">4.1拉伸斜方肌上束</h4>
<p>肩膀和颈椎两侧的肌肉</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="15"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-38d17b192af2504f.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><a href="http://www.miaopai.com/show/~3HuYj0dvSk-yBadI0ZSOA__.htm">视频地址</a></p>
<p>每一侧持续15s，共三组。</p>
<h4 id="42-拉伸斜角肌">4.2 拉伸斜角肌</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="16"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-a19ca50dca323843.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>治疗落枕和拉伸斜方肌上束后胳膊麻木</p>
<p><a href="http://www.miaopai.com/show/nDmkLFiJH9~gx-gzl6-L2Q__.htm">视频地址</a></p>
<p>每一侧15s，共三组。</p>
<h4 id="43-拉伸胸锁乳突肌">4.3 拉伸胸锁乳突肌</h4>
<p>还可以治疗双下巴</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="17"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-eec5a60f35f81ae7.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><a href="http://www.miaopai.com/show/IodqnkF5kFj8fOSEF~fvbw__.htm">视频地址</a></p>
<h4 id="44-拉伸胸大肌">4.4 拉伸胸大肌</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="18"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-a9a38257845fe5ae.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><a href="http://www.miaopai.com/show/WARVgefKyZSOoqbKexRUUA__.htm">视频地址</a></p>
<p>最大强度20s，2-3次</p>
<h3 id="5自我手法">5.自我手法</h3>
<h4 id="51处理颈椎前侧">5.1处理颈椎前侧</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="19"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-f3b414ca9c78f236.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><a href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/uruNQ7VJ_srHDed3z3iKnQ">视频地址</a></p>
<h4 id="52-放松颈椎后侧肌群">5.2 放松颈椎后侧肌群</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="20"><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-51cb96537cfdaf4b.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><a href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/8saJCZgxR-YqLpaulszAzQ">视频地址</a></p>
<p>每组左右各十次，共3组。</p>
<h4 id="53自我手法处理枕骨下缘肌肉">5.3自我手法处理枕骨下缘肌肉</h4>
<p><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/5617055-8aec7bc018162e7c.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image" loading="lazy"><br>
<a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/oh-O_3ZIk3pZpwhi7BkHIQ">视频地址</a></p>
<p>每组6-8次，共三组</p>
<h2 id="四-相关问答">四、相关问答</h2>
<p>1.频率如何控制？</p>
<p>一周3-4次，每次40-60min。可以辅助跑跑步，出出汗</p>
<p>2.脖子咔咔响怎么办？</p>
<p>脖子咔咔不要经常的去咔咔响，偶尔响一下是可以的，说明颈椎的稳定性不好，重点做一下颈椎激活、w上下移动和气场大法</p>
<p>3.如何挑选枕头？</p>
<p><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/25437877">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/25437877</a></p>
]]></content>
